com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface SolverLp

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IGeneratorTool, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SolutionProvider, Solver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SolverLpImpl

    public interface SolverLp
extends Solver
    A representation of the model object 'Lp'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Solver Optimality Tolerance
    • Solver Linear Relaxation
    • Sol Optimality Gap
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getSolverLp()
